This paper discusses the security of wireless networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also involves network infrastructure (cs.NI) and software engineering (cs.SE) in terms of implementing security measures. The paper also touches on social implications (cs.SI) of unsecured Wi-Fi connections and cybercrime (cs.CY) related to hacking.
